div.div: DFT-computed HOMO and LUMO energy values and plots for the model complex 3a-Me (isovalue = 0.03 a.u.). Calculations were performed in the gas phase at MN15L/6-311G* for nonmetal atoms, with the SDD basis set used for Ir. The structure of 3a-Me is also shown, in the approximate orientation used for the orbital depictions.
